\
a) All of the arguments should be \ul scalar\ulnone .\
\
b) In case of \ul vector\ulnone , all of them must have \ul the same length\ulnone .\
\
c) In case of \ul matrix\ulnone , all of them must have \ul the same size\ulnone .\
\
B) 
\f1\b\fs28 surf (X_Var,Y_Var,Z_Var)
\f0\b0\fs24 \
\
This functions plots a three dimensional colored surface.\
\
